<br>
I have never seen recipes for these potions on ANY of the tradeskill or shaman websites, and have only seen the potions sold at vendors.  However, some people will insist that &quot;my guildmate's cousin knows a guy on another server who bought one from so-and-so&quot; and thereby believe it to be a player-made potion.  While I don't think that an alchemist can make them, it could just be that there is no reliable info out there.<br>
<br>
Anyone know of any invis/camo, healing or gate (to bind point) potions that are player-made?<br>
